import { AppBar,Toolbar,IconButton } from "@mui/material"
import MenuIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Menu';
import SearchIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Search'
import { Box } from "@mui/system";



const HeaderMobile = () => {
  return (
    <AppBar>
        <Toolbar>
        <Box>
            <IconButton>
            <MenuIcon/>
            
        </IconButton>
        <IconButton>
            <SearchIcon/>
            
        </IconButton>
        </Box>
        
        </Toolbar>
    </AppBar>
  )
}

export default HeaderMobile
